title: [Icemule Trace, South Road]
description: Various halfling vendors hawking their wares block your way for a moment.  You notice a number of giantmen and dwarves heading north, coins jingling in their pockets.  A twisted, wrought-iron street lamp at the corner keeps an inebriated halfling from meeting the pavement.
